title: #276: "Running" Of The Bulls (@KaiHumphries, @MiloComedy, @Daniel_Sloss)
itunes:title: "Running" Of The Bulls with Kai Humphries, Milo McCabe, and Daniel Sloss
description: Kai Humphries, Milo McCabe, and Daniel Sloss met me at the Abattoir comedian's bar in Edinburgh, Scotland to tell me their harrowing tale of cheating death at the Running of the Bulls in Pamplona, Spain. This was a super fun story! You gotta go to arithegreat.com for this one to look at the pictures. They're CRAZY. Guest appearances by random comedy people trying to distract us with booze.
